      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Laveen Kanal</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:180px;\"><a href=\"https://www.cs.umd.edu/users/kanal/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b5/Laveenkanal.jpg\" width=\"178\" height=\"222\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Laveenkanal.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Laveen Kanal <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Laveen N. Kanal</b>, (born September 29, 1931)<br />\nan American electrical engineer, high technology entrepreneur, educator, and professor emeritus of computer science at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Maryland,_College_Park\">University of Maryland, College Park</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. His research interests include various <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI</a> topics, <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search algorithms</a>, <a href=\"/Pattern_Recognition\" title=\"Pattern Recognition\">pattern recognition</a>, and the application of computational intelligence technologies to image understanding and intelligent tutoring systems <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1960_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1960 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1970_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1970 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1980_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1980 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laveen_Kanal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1960_...\">1960 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laveen_Kanal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1960 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen Kanal</a> (<b>1960</b>). <i>Analysis of some stochastic process arising from a learning model</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Pennsylvania\">University of Pennsylvania</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#RRBush\" title=\"Mathematician\">Robert R. Bush</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen Kanal</a> (<b>1962</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF02289668\">A functional equation analysis of two learning models</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychometrika\">Psychometrika</a>, Vol. 27, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen Kanal</a> (<b>1962</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-1-4684-1716-6_35\">Evaluation of a Class of Pattern-Recognition Networks</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-1-4684-1716-6\">Biological Prototypes and Synthetic Systems</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1970_...\">1970 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laveen_Kanal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1970 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1974</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1055306\">Patterns in pattern recognition: 1968-1974</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TIT\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Information Theory</a>, Vol. 20, No. 6</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/George_Stockman\" title=\"George Stockman\">George C. Stockman</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kyle:M=_C=\">M. C. Kyle</a> (<b>1976</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=360378\">Structural Pattern Recognition Of Carotid Pulse Waves Using A General Waveform Parsing System</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 19, No. 12 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#ARosenfeld\" title=\"Mathematician\">Azriel Rosenfeld</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#JeromeFeldman\" title=\"Mathematician\">Jerome A. Feldman</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a href=\"/Patrick_Winston\" title=\"Patrick Winston\">Patrick H. Winston</a> (<b>1977</b>). <i>AI and Pattern Recognition</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI1977\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 1977</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1979</b>). <i>Problem-Solving Models and Search Strategies for Pattern Recognition</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TPAMI\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence</a>, Vol. 1, No. 2 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1980_...\">1980 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laveen_Kanal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1980 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vipin_Kumar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vipin Kumar (page does not exist)\">Vipin Kumar</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i>Branch &amp; Bound Formulation for Sequential and Parallel Game Tree Searching: Preliminary Results</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI1981\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 1981</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Dana_S._Nau\" title=\"Dana S. Nau\">Dana S. Nau</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vipin_Kumar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vipin Kumar (page does not exist)\">Vipin Kumar</a>,  <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1982</b>). <i>A General Paradigm for A.I. Search Procedures</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-82\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 1982</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#ARosenfeld\" title=\"Mathematician\">Azriel Rosenfeld</a> (eds.) (<b>1982</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/book/9780444863256/progress-in-pattern-recognition\">Progress in Pattern Recognition</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsevier#Imprints\">North Holland</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/George_Stockman\" title=\"George Stockman\">George C. Stockman</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/224377734_Problem_Reduction_Representation_for_the_Linguistic_Analysis_of_Waveforms\">Problem Reduction Representation for the Linguistic Analysis of Waveforms</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TPAMI\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence</a>, Vol. 5, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vipin_Kumar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vipin Kumar (page does not exist)\">Vipin Kumar</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1984</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/4767600\">Parallel Branch-and-Bound Formulations for AND/OR Tree Search</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TPAMI\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence</a>, Vol. 6, No. 6</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Dana_S._Nau\" title=\"Dana S. Nau\">Dana S. Nau</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vipin_Kumar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vipin Kumar (page does not exist)\">Vipin Kumar</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1984</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/0004370284900043\">General Branch and Bound, and its Relation to A* and AO*</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_(journal)\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 23, No. 1</li></ul>\n<p><b>1985</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Leifker:Daniel_B=.html\">Daniel B. Leifker</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1985</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1623687\">A Hybrid SSS*/Alpha-Beta Algorithm for Parallel Search of Game Trees</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI1985\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 1985</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#ARosenfeld\" title=\"Mathematician\">Azriel Rosenfeld</a> (eds.) (<b>1985</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Progress-Pattern-Recognition-Machine-Intelligence/dp/0444877231\">Progress in Pattern Recognition 2</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsevier\">Elsevier</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Uncertainty_AI_1\"></span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Lemmer:John_F=\">John Lemmer</a> (eds.) (<b>1985, 2013</b>). <i>Proceedings of the First Conference on Uncertainty in Artificial Intelligence (1985)</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1304.4182\">arXiv:1304.4182</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Uncertainty_AI_2\"></span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Lemmer:John_F=\">John Lemmer</a> (eds.) (<b>1986, 2013</b>). <i>Proceedings of the Second Conference on Uncertainty in Artificial Intelligence (1986)</i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1304.3859\">arXiv:1304.3859</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Gelsema:Edzard_S=\">Edzard S. Gelsema</a> (eds.) (<b>1986</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/books/pattern-recognition-in-practice-ii/kanal/978-0-444-87877-9\">Pattern Recognition in Practice II</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsevier#Imprints\">North Holland</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Uncertainty_AI_3\"></span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Lemmer:John_F=\">John Lemmer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Levitt:Tod_S=\">Tod Levitt</a> (eds.) (<b>1987, 2013</b>). <i>Proceedings of the Third Conference on Uncertainty in Artificial Intelligence (1987)</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1304.3857\">arXiv:1304.3857</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Uncertainty_AI_4\"></span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Lemmer:John_F=\">John Lemmer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Levitt:Tod_S=\">Tod Levitt</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Shachter:Ross_D=\">Ross Shachter</a> (eds.) (<b>1988, 2013</b>). <i>Proceedings of the Fourth Conference on Uncertainty in Artificial Intelligence (1988)</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1304.3856\">arXiv:1304.3856</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vipin_Kumar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vipin Kumar (page does not exist)\">Vipin Kumar</a> (eds.) (<b>1988</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-1-4613-8788-6\">Search in artificial intelligence</a></i>. Symbolic computation - Artificial intelligence, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Gelsema:Edzard_S=\">Edzard S. Gelsema</a> (eds.) (<b>1988</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/books/pattern-recognition-and-artificial-intelligence-towards-an-integration/kanal/978-0-444-87137-4\">Pattern Recognition and Artificial Intelligence, Towards an Integration</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsevier\">Elsevier</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Uncertainty_AI_5\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Henrion:Max\">Max Henrion</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Lemmer:John_F=\">John Lemmer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Shachter:Ross_D=\">Ross Shachter</a> (eds.) (<b>1989, 2013</b>). <i>Proceedings of the Fifth Conference on Uncertainty in Artificial Intelligence (1989)</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1304.3855\">arXiv:1304.3855</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laveen_Kanal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <span id=\"Uncertainty_AI_6\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Bonissone:Piero_P=\">Piero Bonisson</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Henrion:Max\">Max Henrion</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Lemmer:John_F=\">John Lemmer</a> (eds.) (<b>1990, 2013</b>). <i>Proceedings of the Sixth Conference on Uncertainty in Artificial Intelligence (1990)</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1304.3854\">arXiv:1304.3854</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Hellstrom:Benjamin_J=\">Benjamin J. Hellstrom</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/5726889\">The definition of necessary hidden units in neural networks for combinatorial optimization</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ijcnn/ijcnn1990.html\">IJCNN 1990</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Hellstrom:Benjamin_J=\">Benjamin J. Hellstrom</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/125871\">Knapsack packing networks</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#NN\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Neural Networks</a>, Vol. 3, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Hellstrom:Benjamin_J=\">Benjamin J. Hellstrom</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Asymmetric mean-field neural networks for multiprocessor scheduling</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neural_Networks_(journal)\">Neural Networks</a>, Vol. 5, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=157088\">On Pattern, Categories and Alternate Realities</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pattern_Recognition_Letters\">Pattern Recognition Letters</a>, Vol. 14, No. 3, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lnk.com/prl14.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Gelsema:Edzard_S=\">Edzard S. Gelsema</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (eds.)  (<b>1994</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=561112\">Pattern Recognition in Practice IV:&#160;: Multiple Paradigms, Comparative Studies and Hybrid Systems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsevier\">Elsevier</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Gelsema:Edzard_S=\">Edzard S. Gelsema</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laveen N. Kanal</a> (eds.)  (<b>1997</b>). <i>Pattern Recognition in Practice V</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pattern_Recognition_Letters\">Pattern Recognition Letters</a>, Vol 18, Nos. 11-13</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laveen_Kanal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.cs.